skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: toxic relationship quiz
des: Hi. This quiz is designed to help you determine if you are in a toxic relationship. On a piece of paper, number your answers and respond to each question with, often, sometimes, or rarely. Often is worth 3 points, sometimes is worth 2 points, and rarely is worth one point. At the end of the quiz, ask me for the three scorecard levels, level one, two, or three, to get your quiz results. To get started ask me, ask question one. You can come back to these instructions by asking me for the instructions at any time.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
